                <div id="post-6173" class="post-6173 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-beauty-bests category-the-insider tag-amy-nadine tag-beauty tag-charity tag-cosmetics tag-earth-day tag-fashion tag-green tag-kate-bosworth tag-lauren-conrad tag-makeup tag-makeup-artist tag-natural tag-rachel-bilson tag-style tag-tarte tag-tarte-cosmetics tag-the-beauty-department tag-whitney-port">

                    <h2 class="title"><a href="http://theflossylife.com/2012/04/04/beauty-that-benefits/" rel="bookmark" title="Beauty that&nbsp;Benefits">Beauty that&nbsp;Benefits</a></h2>

                    <a class="date" href="http://theflossylife.com/2012/04/04/beauty-that-benefits/">
                    	<span class="day">4</span>
                    	<span class="month">Apr</span>
                    </a>

                    

                    <div class="entry">
						<p><a href="http://www.fabsugar.com/Pictures-Lauren-Conrads-Style-13596232"><img src="http://theflossylife.files.wordpress.com/2012/04/pictures-lauren-conrads-style.jpg?w=490&#038;h=490" alt="" title="Pictures-Lauren-Conrads-Style" width="490" height="490" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6174" /></a></p>
<p>I&#8217;ve been a fan of Lauren Conrad for a while. I was always a loyal member of &#8220;Team LC,&#8221; if you will. But with all reality show references aside, Conrad&#8217;s success in the style world is easy to see. She&#8217;s got her own clothing line, <a href="http://www.paper-crown.com/" title="Paper Crown" target="_blank">Paper Crown</a>, plus <a onclick="return mugicPopWin(this,event);" oncontextmenu="mugicRightClick(this);" href="http://www.kohls.com/kohlsStore/landingpages/lclaurenconrad.jsp" title="LC Lauren Conrad" target="_blank">LC Lauren Conrad</a> &#8211; an original selection of accessories, clothing, and shoes available only at Kohl&#8217;s. However, my favorite project from this style maven and best-selling author is undoubtedly her beauty-based style blog, <a href="http://thebeautydepartment.com" title="The Beauty Department" target="_blank">The Beauty Department</a>. Dedicated to anything and everything beauty-related, Lauren, makeup artist Amy Nadine, and hair stylist Kristin Ess share videos, tutorials, and photos to give their readers a &#8220;daily dose of pretty.&#8221; </p>
<p><img src="http://theflossylife.files.wordpress.com/2012/04/beautydepartment-logo.jpg?w=490&#038;h=138" alt="" title="beautydepartment logo" width="490" height="138" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6202" /></p>
<p>It&#8217;s hard to believe that it&#8217;s the beginning of April, with Earth Day quickly approaching on the 22nd. <a href="http://thebeautydepartment.com" title="The Beauty Department" target="_blank">The Beauty Department</a> has partnered with <a onclick="return mugicPopWin(this,event);" oncontextmenu="mugicRightClick(this);" href="http://tartecosmetics.com/" title="tarte cosmetics" target="_blank">tarte cosmetics</a> to celebrate the holiday with an eco-chic, limited-edition Earth Day collection called the &#8220;down to earth&#8221; kit. Priced at $49, it&#8217;s exclusively available for purchase <a href="http://rstyle.me/hfezbgmcsn" title="here" target="_blank">here</a>. </p>
<p><img src="http://theflossylife.files.wordpress.com/2012/04/earth-day-set.jpg?w=490&#038;h=378" alt="" title="Earth Day set" width="490" height="378" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-6187" /></p>
<p>Included in this kit are a few of Amy Nadine&#8217;s favorite tarte products, including the LipSurgence™ lip tint; gifted Amazonian clay smart mascara; Amazonian clay 12-hour blush; and multiplEYE™ liquid liner. Take it from this popular celeb makeup artist, who&#8217;s worked with clients including Kate Bosworth, Rachel Bilson, and Whitney Port, that tarte cosmetics are some of the best out there. And while I&#8217;m no beauty genius myself, I am a fan of tarte&#8217;s <a href="http://rstyle.me/ikanmcsn" title="emphasEYES™ inner rim brightener" target="_blank">emphasEYES™ inner rim brightener</a> and <a href="http://rstyle.me/hejx8dmcsn" title="aqua-gel eyeliners" target="_blank">aqua-gel eyeliners</a>.</p>
<p>Not only is tarte combining these four fab products into one kit, but they&#8217;re also donating 20% of all proceeds to The Beauty Department&#8217;s charity of choice, <a href="http://winetowater.org/" title="Wine to Water" target="_blank">Wine to Water</a>. This nonprofit focuses on supplying adequate water to needy people worldwide, already successfully implementing clean water in nine countries since 2004. Wine to Water even offers a unique wine selection, with $7.00 from every bottle sold going back to support their efforts. That sounds like a charity even I can back.</p>
<p>So get pretty and help out in the spirit of this coming Earth Day. Who knew you could do both at once? </p>
<div class="sharedaddy sd-sharing-enabled"></div>												<p>Tags: <a href="http://theflossylife.com/tag/amy-nadine/" rel="tag">Amy Nadine</a>, <a href="http://theflossylife.com/tag/beauty/" rel="tag">beauty</a>, <a href="http://theflossylife.com/tag/charity/" rel="tag">charity</a>, <a href="http://theflossylife.com/tag/cosmetics/" rel="tag">cosmetics</a>, <a href="http://theflossylife.com/tag/earth-day/" rel="tag">Earth Day</a>, <a href="http://theflossylife.com/tag/fashion/" rel="tag">fashion</a>, <a href="http://theflossylife.com/tag/green/" rel="tag">green</a>, <a href="http://theflossylife.com/tag/kate-bosworth/" rel="tag">Kate Bosworth</a>, <a href="http://theflossylife.com/tag/lauren-conrad/" rel="tag">Lauren Conrad</a>, <a href="http://theflossylife.com/tag/makeup/" rel="tag">makeup</a>, <a href="http://theflossylife.com/tag/makeup-artist/" rel="tag">makeup artist</a>, <a href="http://theflossylife.com/tag/natural/" rel="tag">natural</a>, <a href="http://theflossylife.com/tag/rachel-bilson/" rel="tag">Rachel Bilson</a>, <a href="http://theflossylife.com/tag/style/" rel="tag">style</a>, <a href="http://theflossylife.com/tag/tarte/" rel="tag">tarte</a>, <a href="http://theflossylife.com/tag/tarte-cosmetics/" rel="tag">tarte cosmetics</a>, <a href="http://theflossylife.com/tag/the-beauty-department/" rel="tag">The Beauty Department</a>, <a href="http://theflossylife.com/tag/whitney-port/" rel="tag">Whitney Port</a></p>						                    </div>

                    <div class="post-meta">

