<p>So whether you&#8217;ve got your eye on denim, silk, lace, or leather, at least one pair of shorts is probably a smart investment for spring. And regardless of if it&#8217;s by a designer you like, trying on shorts is crucial to a proper fit. Just don&#8217;t let anyone tell you that a white stripe across your butt looks good, because someone <del datetime="2012-04-04T15:31:48+00:00">like me</del> will eventually speak the truth.     </p>
