                    			<span class="body"><a href="http://theflossylife.com/category/beauty-bests/" title="View all posts in Beauty Bests" rel="category tag">Beauty Bests</a>, <a href="http://theflossylife.com/category/the-insider/" title="View all posts in The Insider" rel="category tag">The Insider</a></span>
