                <div id="post-5785" class="post-5785 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-street-style category-as-seen-on category-the-insider tag-marc-jacobs tag-lauren-conrad tag-marc-by-marc-jacobs tag-fashion tag-style tag-fashion-trends tag-celebrity-fashion tag-trends tag-kate-middleton tag-jennifer-aniston tag-michelle-williams tag-vera-wang tag-peplum tag-peplum-dress tag-peplum-trend tag-formal-occasions tag-miss-selfridge">

                    <h2 class="title"><a href="http://theflossylife.com/2012/03/29/peplum-party/" rel="bookmark" title="Peplum&nbsp;Party">Peplum&nbsp;Party</a></h2>

                    <a class="date" href="http://theflossylife.com/2012/03/29/peplum-party/">
                    	<span class="day">29</span>
                    	<span class="month">Mar</span>
                    </a>

                    

                    <div class="entry">
						<p>Peplum, or more specifically &#8220;a flared ruffle attached to the waist of a jacket, dress, or blouse,&#8221; has become quite the popular trend. It&#8217;s actually a recycled one, having been big in the 40&#8242;s and again in the late 1980&#8242;s to the tone of shoulder pads and glitter. A statement piece in itself, peplum can often be tricky to pull off. When worn incorrectly, it can make your hips look big, and critics have claimed it&#8217;s too fussy and costume-inspired. On the brighter side, however, peplum holds the power to accentuate your figure. And that&#8217;s more of what we&#8217;re all looking for, right?</p>
<p>Vera Wang, who incorporated this look into her spring 2012 runway show, is a designer who still backs this updated trend. She recently stated, &#8220;A peplum is a play on proportion to make the waist look smaller.&#8221; </p>
<p><a href="http://news.instyle.com/2012/03/08/peplum-celebrity-kate-middleton-jennifer-aniston-more/"><img src="http://theflossylife.files.wordpress.com/2012/03/030812-peplum-kate-middleton-623.jpg?w=490&#038;h=314" alt="" title="030812-Peplum-kate-middleton-623" width="490" height="314" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5786" /></a></p>
<p>So whether you want to look royal like Kate or as effortlessly chic as Blake, hop on the peplum bandwagon ASAP. This style can work for both casual and formal occasions, as proved by Michelle Williams at this year&#8217;s Oscars ceremony. I purchased <a href="http://www.polyvore.com/alice_olivia_ella_striped_stretch-jersey/thing?id=32293648" title="this" target="_blank">this</a> Alice+Olivia tee last year and frequently paired it with red jeans or a black pencil skirt. It&#8217;s proved to a versatile <em>and</em> classic asset to my closet.  </p>
<p>Decide if this trend is right for you by taking a look at some of my favorite peplum pieces:</p>
<div align="center"><a href="http://rstyle.me/fxa9fcmcsn" title="$94 Aqua Camilla Shaped Peplum Structured Bandeau Dress" target="_blank">$94 Aqua Camilla Shaped Peplum Structured Bandeau Dress</a></div>
<p><img src="http://theflossylife.files.wordpress.com/2012/03/image1xl1.jpg?w=490" alt="" title="image1xl"   class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5813" /></p>
<div align="center"><a href="http://rstyle.me/g7gpammcsn" title="$33 LC Lauren Conrad Chiffon Peplum Vest" target="_blank">$33 LC Lauren Conrad Chiffon Peplum Vest</a></div>
<p><a href="http://theflossylife.files.wordpress.com/2012/03/965558_maple_sugar.jpg"><img src="http://theflossylife.files.wordpress.com/2012/03/965558_maple_sugar.jpg?w=490" alt="" title="965558_Maple_Sugar"   class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-5841" /></a></p>
<div align="center"><a href="http://rstyle.me/hd9jzimcsn" title="$198 Marc by Marc Jacobs Flavin Stripe Peplum Top " target="_blank">$198 Marc by Marc Jacobs Flavin Stripe Peplum Top </a></div>
<p><a href="http://theflossylife.files.wordpress.com/2012/03/1287901_fpx-tif.jpg"><img src="http://theflossylife.files.wordpress.com/2012/03/1287901_fpx-tif.jpg?w=240&#038;h=300" alt="" title="1287901_fpx.tif" width="240" height="300" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-5818" /></a></p>
<div align="center"><a href="http://rstyle.me/g77w9smcsn" title=" $57 Miss Selfridge Black Peplum Skirt" target="_blank"><br />
$57 Miss Selfridge Black Peplum Skirt</a></div>
