92_926961200374_21306985_42057998_1862233864_n.jpg" class="aligncenter" width="300" height="300" /></a></div>
</div><div id="text-5" class="widget widget_text">			<div class="textwidget"><div align="center">The Flossy Life is written by Laurie Street, a 20-something retail junkie, neurotic mother to deux fabulous frenchies, and lover of all things “flossy” (i.e. anything Yves Saint Laurent, available at Barney’s, or created by Mary-Kate and Ashley Olsen). A professional packer, she is obsessed with good food but doesn’t cook; battles an ongoing addiction to reality TV; sometimes (always) laughs when others embarrass themselves in public; and loves to travel but never remembers the way. Writing for whatever it is that makes your life flossy – and praying that it’s nothing involving cubic zirconia, blue tropical drinks, Miss Me jeans, or hotels without valet.</div>
